<p><span>Access the CIP Germplasm Ordering System. (To open the ordering system in another window, click </span><a href="https://research.cip.cgiar.org/smta/search1.php"><span>here</span></a><span>.) </span></p>
<p><span>Select descriptors to use to find material, then click </span><span>Proceed </span><span>(at the bottom of the list).</span><br /><span><br class="kix-line-break" /></span><img height="393px;" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/unPrfwnyrtHgVUHObF2rqjRXne_nhOO-HhRJGH1yRpA1sgQXIArzUBKXkr5rJkJkWf9y8pqnfRdt4i9ysZtxISS54HWKabCBXf-4vb0LeJ1x2fdHhA" width="502px;" /><br /><br /> <span>Enter a value for each descriptor, then click </span><span>Proceed</span><span>.<br class="kix-line-break" /></span><img height="184px;" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/NZANYnVAvkZLxexdal34knAqr5IEY4xGzBxLlnxqg_fLQV1pQSAyl9VlVZHqz3ypCELapaR-YpCAnqPAVZ3_E5euGWn0nATdJI4Tk2zyEbalPrZ6Zw" width="497px;" /></p>
<p><span>The system lists the material that matches your descriptors. </span><img height="139px;" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Of5SqEQCjLgxaV2KMELFA8JdyX_QMTz8Y8IRRNOSz1X3VMUDrgUynal5KbJH-Fz0LGVFRo5EYFatU8yoAAaHsKSWeXUafcsXUICP-k7meIMz-PE_Lw" width="530px;" /></p>
<p><span> </span></p>
<p><span>To select material, click its box under </span><span>Add to cart</span><span>. When you’ve finished making selections, click </span><span>Next</span><span> (above the list of material).<br class="kix-line-break" /></span><img height="169px;" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/mUrLHLTW4PfcfZp5hkHVnJkd7OEBy9kM8J0qOCSEK_ccG4k92qh_dMw2nQFSXi4hQXdYbJm4MOOCdqS0RTO_GiH0O5wtdZ4lDFJRWPeUUrhH6_A8gQ" width="560px;" /> <span> </span></p>
<p><span>View the material in your cart, then click </span><span>Next</span><span>.<br class="kix-line-break" /></span><img height="80px;" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/nSf6HwgjqHXHfY_TM3jRNCYD0ROql7aVZyooQxCzjTC_29pqwKadUTdEBI_X9FKKewRFW5eAoivF4Yie-JoffHcxF0Nmf_k6iokaUH0yIIujfeLUBQ" width="586px;" /><br /><span></span></p>
<p><span>On the User Registration page, enter your user name and password, then click </span><span>Submit</span><span>. (If you are a new user, click the </span><span>New User </span><span>link, enter your information, then click </span><span>Submit</span><span>.)<br class="kix-line-break" /></span><img height="186px;" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/BqX7V_aqTXcsLEat8VOs9O6NyN25vBSxI3Zhg2OHD_ehpnjnY256fQshA-amBdQQiOjm6OWEEqgn0sq3X-bPOsjn6AkBCc-VXE0HSaHAdPi_MjllRg" width="206px;" /><br /><span></span></p>
<p><span>When your cart reappears, click </span><span>Next</span><span>.<br class="kix-line-break" /></span><br /><span>Review your order information to be sure it’s correct. Make any necessary changes. </span><img height="315px;" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/CvU32pB3JAiiYssNmp4fhoXRMwy1MCgF3CHtUlEmLceNZj3bf8E_7uFjqKAZYFcBK0qK8UAuQKqd2xvLrLvD7VLKKltqwjQ1lMB7BksebdivgzIU5Q" width="496px;" /><br /><span></span></p>
<p><span>In the middle of the page, indicate how your material will be used.</span><img height="216px;" src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/xBo__A7xt0KhWFbQTBxGW3dpHdxKJGCUCgf0pU9SXgEM84wiyLE0bSWuySn1v4iJLkeOUESlL6HIt5Qz2nRbdHIeAXqGlyz3QE1vqcw5XUlM0shgMg" width="289px;" /><br /><span></span></p>
<p><span>Read the Standard Material Transfer Agreement (SMTA), and then click </span><span>I read</span><span>.<br class="kix-line-break" /></span><br /><span>If your germplasm is for breeding, research, training for agriculture, or cultivation:</span></p>
<ol>
<li style="list-style-type: lower-alpha; "><span>Select the method of acceptance.</span></li>
<li style="list-style-type: lower-alpha; "><span>Select the form of payments.</span></li>
<li style="list-style-type: lower-alpha; "><span>View the non-privacy agreement, then click </span><span>I agree</span><span>.</span></li>
<li style="list-style-type: lower-alpha; "><span></span><img height="226px;" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/zeiZd8oWAbvIIwSzSxsW9ADjAvBPCxTkqreNz79n6Pm4P610sS_oeP8e98iYlqryU3yWCPHjPS0w-mYNnMhFQDmYiorCEcuFw9pmrOIHFc9ZOYcaXQ" width="175px;" /></li>
</ol>
<p><span>Click </span><span>I agree to the above conditions</span><span>, and then click </span><span>Submit</span><span>.</span><span></span></p>
<p><span>You will receive an email to confirm that your order has been received.</span></p>